  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/05ac835b70d6437291c8a862fb5d55ed.avif?t=1730274664\" width=616 height=81 /></span><br><br>Experience the fast-paced thrill of ΔVØID, a first-person endless runner with a head turning twist–you rotate the world around you to avoid obstacles.<br><br>Feel yourself getting better with each 90-degree rotation as you twist and bend your way through 9 visually striking, procedurally generated environments. <br><br><i>Prepare for your delicious demise... </i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/f8482fcda919dec124ca2a7552c9a66a.avif?t=1730274664\" width=616 height=81 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rotate the world around you in 90 degree increments. It's wall-running redefined.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/7d30a0b15edd24ca1ea320b4ea59374d.poster.avif?t=1730274664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/7d30a0b15edd24ca1ea320b4ea59374d.webm?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/7d30a0b15edd24ca1ea320b4ea59374d.mp4?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Experience unique \"Transition Circuits\", the boss-like final challenge before advancing each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/8310abf870979bf451525f0c5062e4d8.poster.avif?t=1730274664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/8310abf870979bf451525f0c5062e4d8.webm?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/8310abf870979bf451525f0c5062e4d8.mp4?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Steadily take on more challenging obstacles and gravity-defying stunts.<br></li><li>Combine moves in satisfying and creative ways. <br></li><li>Select one of 4 speeds to do it all again, but faster!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/135e370a98267815fd833ab1c9765faa.poster.avif?t=1730274664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/135e370a98267815fd833ab1c9765faa.webm?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/135e370a98267815fd833ab1c9765faa.mp4?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Unlock \"Quantum Stride\", stack multipliers, and climb the leaderboards.<br></li><li>Choose between 3 game modes, each featuring its own leaderboard.<br></li><li>Explore mesmerising and atmospheric environments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/cd64ecc80cf0ec1a8b4372f76d5d8f8d.poster.avif?t=1730274664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/cd64ecc80cf0ec1a8b4372f76d5d8f8d.webm?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622220/extras/cd64ecc80cf0ec1a8b4372f76d5d8f8d.mp4?t=1730274664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Enjoy a meticulously curated soundtrack to match the fast-paced action.<br></li><li>Unlock <strong>40+ achievements</strong>.</li></ul>",
